Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average resolution time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Minimum time to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total time it takes 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to be done before 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time for 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in the variant with the highest performance score
